# Deployment Policy

**Never deploy Firebase Hosting** from the agent or local CLI (`firebase deploy --only hosting`, `web:deploy`, `web:deploy-fresh`). Production web hosting is deployed automatically via GitHub Actions on merge to `main`.

When the user asks to "deploy" web changes: **commit and push** so CI deploys hosting.

Functions deploy (`yarn nx run functions:deploy`) is allowed when explicitly requested. Admin deploys via Vercel on push — do not run Vercel CLI unless asked.
